<F P=102>  OW1903145294 Beijing XINHUA in English 1249 GMT 19 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW1903145294 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Shanghai, March 19 (XINHUA) -- Ecuador President 
Sixto Duran-Ballen ended his visit here and left this afternoon 
for Xian, capital of northwest China's Shaanxi Province, by 
special plane. 
  Vice-Mayor of Shanghai Sha Lin and Director of the Shanghai 
Municipal Office of Foreign Affairs Xu Zhaochun saw the Ecuador 
guests off at the airport. 
  This morning, Sixto Duran-Ballen and his party visited the 
developing Pudong new area in Shanghai and thought highly of the 
