entrepreneurs will take an active part in investing in the place. 
  Duran-Ballen and his party also visited the building site of 
an export centre in the Pudong new area and the Jiangnan 
shipyards. 
  Duran-Ballen's wife toured several parts of the city and 
visited a silk dyeing and printing mill this morning. 

