Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] At noon yesterday [11 March] in Beijing's Fujian 
Provincial Guild, provincial leading members -- including Jia 
Qinglin, You Dexin, He Shaochuan, Yuan Qitong, Huang Changxi, 
Shi Qingmao -- and old comrade Lin Qing cordially met with 
deputies to the National People's Congress [NPC] and members of 
