Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, March 22 (CNS) -- Deputy of the NPC and 
director of the Party Literature Research Centre Mr. Pang 
Xianzhi said that Deng Xiaoping's Selected Works (1938-1965) and 
(1975-1982) would be renamed The First and Second Volume 
