<F P=103> SK2303123794 </F>
<F P=104>  Jinan Shandong People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Summary] The cable television station of the Jinan Railway 
Bureau officially began broadcasting on 22 March. This 
television station was built in 1993 with the approval of the 
Ministry of Radio, Film, and Television. It adopts an optical 
fiber cable transmission system, which is currently the most 
advanced transmission system. In the second half of this year, 
people will be able to receive 30 programs, which will be 
transmitted mainly to the Jinan area. 

