<F P=100> NATIONAL AFFAIRS </F>
<F P=101> Political &amp; Social </F>
<H3> <TI>   Party Building, Leadership Stressed at Central Forum </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  HK2303125394 Beijing RENMIN RIBAO in Chinese 9 Mar 94 p 5 </F>
<F P=103> HK2303125394 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing RENMIN RIBAO </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Chinese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [By Zhong Jianyan (6988 0256 0917): "Strengthen Party </F>
Building and Leadership"] 
  [Text] The Party Building Research Office of the CPC 
Central Committee's Organization Department held a seminar a few 
days ago. More than 20 leaders, experts, and scholars who have 
long been engaged in the party's practical work attended the 
seminar, studied Comrade Deng Xiaoping's theory of building 
socialism with Chinese characteristics and the decision of the 
Third Plenary Session of the 14th CPC Central Committee, and 
probed the theory of further strengthening party leadership over 
socialist economy, politics, and culture with Chinese 
characteristics. Those attending the seminar held the consensus 
that Comrade Deng Xiaoping's theory of building socialism with 
Chinese characteristics inherited and developed 
Marxism-Leninism-Mao Zedong Thought and that strengthening and 
improving party leadership constituted an important component of 
the theory of building socialism with Chinese characteristics. 
It is necessary to vigorously, comprehensively, and correctly 
study, publicize, and implement the theory of building socialism 
with Chinese characteristics and the party's basic line, and 
apply them in seeking unity of thought within the whole party 
and guide all fields of work. 
  As China's reform and opening up has entered a very 
important 
historic period, the attendants pointed out at the seminar, we 
must follow the party's basic line and theories, seize the 
favorable opportunity, exert ourselves, and strive to push 
forward China's socialist cause. In view of the problems of 
mass concern, the attendants made many good proposals: The 
socialist market economic system, which is combined with the 
basic socialist system, is different from the capitalist market 
economic system. While establishing the socialist market 
economic system, it is absolutely necessary to consciously 
maintain and uphold the predominant position of public ownership 
and distribution according to work and resist the ideas and 
actions which attempt to shake the predominance of these two 
factors. "Emancipation and development of the productive 
forces, elimination of exploitation and polarization, and 
attainment of the ultimate goal of common prosperity" proposed 
by Deng Xiaoping is the scientific expression of the essence of 
socialism and integrated thinking, which cannot be separated or 
even willfully quoted out of context. The CPC is the core of 
leadership for the building of socialism with Chinese 
characteristics, while the masses of people, centered on 
workers, peasants, and intellectuals, are the vital force for 
this grand cause. It is very important to strengthen the 
party's ideological, theoretical, and political building, launch 
protracted struggles against corruption, and maintain purity of 
the party's ranks to ensure that leadership of all levels is 
firmly in the hands of those loyal to contemporary Chinese 
Marxism. If we weaken party leadership, neglect party building, 
forsake the mass line, diminish the status of master of the 
working class, divorce ourselves from the peasants, and slacken 
efforts to build socialist spiritual civilization, our cause 
will suffer and even meet with failure. We must firmly bear in 
mind the historic lesson drawn from being hard on one aspect but 
soft on the other, do two types of work simultaneously and pay 
equal attention to both, and ensure the healthy growth of 
China's reform and construction. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

<DOC>
<DOCNO> FBIS3-3908 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "drchi057_k_94013" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-CHI-94-057 </AU>
Document Type:Daily Report 
<DATE1>  23 Mar 1994 </DATE1>

</HEADER>

<F P=100> NATIONAL AFFAIRS </F>
<F P=101> Political &amp; Social </F>
<H3> <TI>   Fifty Percent of Enterprises Guilty of Illegal Practices </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  HK2403014694 Beijing ZHONGGUO XINWEN SHE in English 1411 GMT 
23 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> HK2403014694 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing ZHONGGUO XINWEN SHE </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, March 23 (CNS) -- A taxation inspection of 
enterprises last year discovered various kinds of illegal tax- 
related practices involving RMB [Renminbi] 15.4 billion with RMB 
10 billion being recovered by the state. 
  Tax evasion has become rampant in the country with more than 
50 percent of all enterprises and individually-owned business 
households found guilty of such practices. Some enterprises 
were found to have evaded taxes of more than RMB 1 million. 
Last year saw the industrial and commercial tax evasion being 
put at RMB 6.18 billion, evasion of income tax RMB 1.85 billion 
and evasion of payment for key items' construction as well as 
for budgetary regulation RMB 1.187 billion, adding up to RMB 
9.22 billion and constituting 63.4 percent of all illegal funds. 
  Another serious problem was the deduction of sums of state 
revenue. 
  Rampant money-collecting by administrative departments and 
institutions was also serious. According to experts, there was 
an urgent need to establish a supervisory mechanism for handling 
such illegal matters in the country. 

</TEXT>

